# AI-Powered Credit Card Fraud Detection

## Features
- Fraud Detection using Random Forest
- Exploratory Data Analysis
- Fraud Analytics Dashboard
- ROC Curve
- Confusion Matrix
- Feature Importance
- Streamlit Deployment

